import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import '../styles/Dashboard.css'; const Dashboard = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [activeFilter, setActiveFilter] = useState('Tất cả'); const [activeView, setActiveView] = useState('grid'); const [bookmarkedTests, setBookmarkedTests] = useState([1, 4]); const stats = [ { label: 'Bài thi đã hoàn thành', value: '23', icon: 'fas fa-clipboard-check', color: 'blue', trend: '+3 từ tuần trước', trendUp: true }, { label: 'Điểm trung bình', value: '7.5/10', icon: 'fas fa-star', color: 'green', trend: '+0.5 điểm', trendUp: true }, { label: 'Thời gian học', value: '45h', icon: 'fas fa-clock', color: 'amber', trend: '+8h tuần này', trendUp: true }, { label: 'Mục tiêu tiếp theo', value: 'IELTS 8.0', icon: 'fas fa-trophy', color: 'purple', progress: 65 } ]; const filters = ['Tất cả', 'IELTS', 'TOEFL', 'Business', 'Academic']; const tests = [ { id: 1, title: 'IELTS Academic Practice Test - Full Test', difficulty: 'medium', difficultyText: 'Intermediate', duration: '180 phút', rating: '4.8 (1,234)', skills: ['listening', 'reading', 'writing', 'speaking'], category: 'ielts', featured: true, recommended: true }, { id: 2, title: 'TOEFL iBT Reading & Listening', difficulty: 'medium', difficultyText: 'Intermediate', duration: '120 phút', rating: '4.6 (892)', skills: ['listening', 'reading'], category: 'toefl' }, { id: 3, title: 'Business English Communication', difficulty: 'hard', difficultyText: 'Advanced', duration: '90 phút', rating: '4.9 (567)', skills: ['listening', 'reading', 'writing'], category: 'business' }, { id: 4, title: 'Academic Writing Skills Test', difficulty: 'medium', difficultyText: 'Intermediate', duration: '60 phút', rating: '4.7 (734)', skills: ['reading', 'writing'], category: 'academic' }, { id: 5, title: 'IELTS Speaking Mock Test', difficulty: 'easy', difficultyText: 'Beginner', duration: '15 phút', rating: '4.8 (1,023)', skills: ['speaking'], category: 'ielts' }, { id: 6, title: 'General English Proficiency', difficulty: 'easy', difficultyText: 'Beginner', duration: '45 phút', rating: '4.5 (456)', skills: ['listening', 'reading'], category: 'toefl' } ]; const recentTests = [ { title: 'IELTS Academic Reading', date: '2 ngày trước', score: '8.0/10' }, { title: 'TOEFL Listening Practice', date: '5 ngày trước', score: '7.5/10' }, { title: 'Business English Writing', date: '1 tuần trước', score: '6.5/10' } ]; const toggleBookmark = (testId) => { setBookmarkedTests(prev => prev.includes(testId) ? prev.filter(id => id !== testId) : [...prev, testId] ); }; const getSkillIcon = (skill) => { const icons = { listening: 'fas fa-headphones', reading: 'fas fa-book-open', writing: 'fas fa-pen', speaking: 'fas fa-microphone' }; return icons[skill]; }; return (
